OP13-OP13-001 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (001)
OP13-OP13-001 normal.description: [DON!! x1] [On Your Opponent's Attack] If you have 5 or less active DON!! cards, you may rest any number of your DON!! cards. For every DON!! card rested this way, this Leader or up to 1 of your "Straw Hat Crew" type Characters gains +2000 power during this battle.

OP13-OP13-001 parallel.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (001) (Alternate Art)
OP13-OP13-001 parallel.description: [DON!! x1] [On Your Opponent's Attack] If you have 5 or less active DON!! cards, you may rest any number of your DON!! cards. For every DON!! card rested this way, this Leader or up to 1 of your "Straw Hat Crew" type Characters gains +2000 power during this battle.

OP13-OP13-002 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace (002)
OP13-OP13-002 normal.description:
[On Your Opponent's Attack] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Give up to 1 of your opponent's Leader or Character cards 2000 power during this battle.
[DON!! x1] [Once Per Turn] When you take damage or your Character with 6000 base power or more is K.O.'d, draw 1 card.

OP13-OP13-002 parallel.name: Portgas.D.Ace (002) (Alternate Art)
OP13-OP13-002 parallel.description:
[On Your Opponent's Attack] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Give up to 1 of your opponent's Leader or Character cards 2000 power during this battle.
[DON!! x1] [Once Per Turn] When you take damage or your Character with 6000 base power or more is K.O.'d, draw 1 card.

OP13-OP13-003 normal.name: Gol.D.Roger (003)
OP13-OP13-003 normal.description:
If you have any DON!! cards on your field, 1 DON!! card placed during your DON!! Phase is given to your Leader.
If you have 9 or less DON!! cards on your field, give this Leader 2000 power.

OP13-OP13-004 normal.name: Sabo (004)
OP13-OP13-004 normal.description:
If you have 4 or more Life cards, give this Leader 1000 power.
[DON!! x1] If you have a Character with a cost of 8 or more, your Leader and all of your Characters gain +1000 power.

OP13-OP13-004 parallel.name: Sabo (004) (Alternate Art)
OP13-OP13-004 parallel.description:
If you have 4 or more Life cards, give this Leader 1000 power.
[DON!! x1] If you have a Character with a cost of 8 or more, your Leader and all of your Characters gain +1000 power.

OP13-OP13-017 normal.name: Monkey.D.Dragon
OP13-OP13-017 normal.description: [Once Per Turn] If your "Revolutionary Army" type Character would be removed from the field by your opponent's effect, you may give this Character 2000 power during this turn instead.

OP13-OP13-063 normal.name: Kouzuki Oden
OP13-OP13-063 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Play] If you have any DON!! cards given, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.

OP13-OP13-067 normal.name: Scopper Gaban
OP13-OP13-067 normal.description: [On Play] If your Leader's type includes "Roger Pirates", draw 2 cards and trash 1 card from your hand. Then, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.

OP13-OP13-076 normal.name: Divine Departure
OP13-OP13-076 normal.description:
[Main] You may rest 5 of your DON!! cards: If you have any DON!! cards given, give up to 1 of your opponent's Characters 8000 power during this turn.
[Counter] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +3000 power during this battle.

OP13-OP13-079 normal.name: Imu
OP13-OP13-079 normal.description:
Under the rules of this game, you cannot include Events with a cost of 2 or more in your deck and at the start of the game, play up to 1 [Mary Geoise] type Stage card from your deck.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 of your [Celestial Dragons] type Characters or 1 card from your hand: Draw 1 card.

OP13-OP13-079 parallel.name: Imu (Alternate Art)
OP13-OP13-079 parallel.description:
Under the rules of this game, you cannot include Events with a cost of 2 or more in your deck and at the start of the game, play up to 1 [Mary Geoise] type Stage card from your deck.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 of your [Celestial Dragons] type Characters or 1 card from your hand: Draw 1 card.

OP13-OP13-098 normal.name: Never Existed... in the First Place...
OP13-OP13-098 normal.description:
[Main] You may rest 1 of your DON!! cards: If your Leader is [Imu], K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Stages with a cost of 7.
[Counter] If your Leader is [Imu], up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +4000 power during this battle.

OP13-OP13-100 normal.name: Jewelry Bonney (100)
OP13-OP13-100 normal.description: [Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] This effect can be activated when you play a Character with a [Trigger]. Give up to 2 rested DON!! cards to 1 of your Leader or Character cards.
